{"tid":1228261,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「孔曰成仁，孟曰取義」，感謝捨身取義的義士，願你的靈魂長存於天地之間","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:53:23.000Z","uid":187549,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"173b704d07824e0940748b8870e94eab1d7f9f03","tid":1228261,"uid":187549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:41:16.000Z","msg":"「志士仁人，無求生以害仁，有殺身以成仁。」<br />\n<br />\n小時候背誦的語句，萬萬想不到會在今天的香港出現。<br />\n<br />\n義士，願你的靈魂長存於天地之間，願你的捨身取義，能為香港換來自由。<br />\n<br />\n生命誠可貴，請不要再有犧牲者，我地明天要好好保護自己。<br />\n為香港，為自由，香港人加油！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URrWUkh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURrWUkh.png&h=f9aca5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uvZ5Nm2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuvZ5Nm2.jpg&h=44a59a7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2fb6ac34356a119ba6ebeb4338fac6bb79c63bf1","tid":1228261,"uid":187549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aQCSsT4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaQCSsT4.png&h=780b912e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}